            "title": "Websites",
            "id": 71324,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Vamos dar uma olhada em como os links funcionam para combinar <strong>páginas da web</strong> em <strong>sites</strong>. Clique em <code>Take a break!</code> para usar o link.</p><webview version=\"2\" visible-if=\"always\" content=\"&lt;!doctype html&gt;&#xA;&lt;head&gt;&#xA; &lt;style&gt;&#xA;  body {&#xA;   background-image: linear-gradient(45deg, #a1c4fd, #c2e9fb);&#xA;   text-align: center;&#xA;   font-family: &quot;Verdana&quot;, Sans-serif;&#xA;  }&#xA;  &#xA;  img {&#xA;   margin: 40px;&#xA;   height: 40px;&#xA;   width: 150px;&#xA;  }&#xA;  &#xA;  h1 {&#xA;   margin-top: 30px;&#xA;  }&#xA;  &#xA;  h3 {&#xA;   margin: 20px;&#xA;   font-weight: normal;&#xA;  }&#xA;  &#xA;  p {&#xA;   margin-top: 80px;&#xA;   margin-left: 30px;&#xA;   margin-right: 30px;&#xA;   padding: 20px;&#xA;   background-color: DimGray;&#xA;  }&#xA; &lt;/style&gt;&#xA;&lt;/head&gt;&#xA;&lt;body&gt;&#xA; &lt;h1&gt;Need five?&lt;/h1&gt; &lt;a&#xA;  href=&quot;https://google.com&quot;&gt;Take a&#xA;  break!&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/body&gt;&#xA;&lt;/html&gt;\" /></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Links",
            "id": 70808,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para começar a criar um link, adicionamos o texto entre as tags <code>&lt;a&gt;</code> e <code>&lt;/a&gt;</code>. Isso ainda não destacará o texto.</p><p><code>&lt;a&gt;</code> significa tag \"Anchor\".</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"html\" name=\"index.html\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"a\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"Learn to Code\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"a\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"3\" /><option startIndex=\"16\" endIndex=\"20\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>&lt;a&gt;</code> seguido de <code>&lt;/a&gt;</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Links",
            "id": 70811,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para vincular o texto a uma página da web, adicionamos <code>href=\"\"</code> junto com um Localizador Uniforme de Recursos (<strong>URL</strong>). <code>href</code> é a abreviação de \"referência de hipertexto\".</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"html\" name=\"index.html\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"a\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"href\" class=\"attr\" /><text value=\"=\" /><text value=\"&quot;https://mimo.org&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"Learn to Code\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"a\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"3\" endIndex=\"7\" /><option startIndex=\"7\" endIndex=\"8\" /><option startIndex=\"8\" endIndex=\"26\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>href</code> seguido de <code>=</code> e finalmente <code>\"https://mimo.org\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Attributes",
            "id": 70809,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p><code>href</code> é um <strong>atributo</strong>. Todos os atributos têm duas coisas em comum: eles fornecem informações extras e vão dentro da tag de abertura.</p><p>Os atributos são adicionados após o nome da tag e antes do sinal de fechamento <code>&gt;</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"html\" name=\"index.html\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"a\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"href\" class=\"attr\" /><text value=\"=\" /><text value=\"&quot;https://mimo.org&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"Learn to Code\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"a\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"3\" endIndex=\"7\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>href</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Equal sign",
            "id": 70810,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Nós vinculamos a uma página da web adicionando <code>=</code> após o atributo e uma URL como valor entre aspas.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"html\" name=\"index.html\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"&lt;!doctype html&gt;\" class=\"meta\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"html\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"body\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"a\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"href\" class=\"attr\" /><text value=\"=\" /><text value=\"&quot;https://mimo.org&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"Learn to Code\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"a\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"body\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"html\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"40\" endIndex=\"41\" /><option startIndex=\"41\" endIndex=\"42\" /><option startIndex=\"42\" endIndex=\"58\" /><option startIndex=\"58\" endIndex=\"59\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>=</code> seguido de <code>\"</code> e depois <code>https://mimo.org</code>, <code>\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Create a link",
            "id": 117993,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Crie uma tag de abertura <code>&lt;a&gt;</code> com o atributo <code>href</code> definido como <code>\"https://mimo.org\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"html\" name=\"index.html\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"a\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"href\" class=\"attr\" /><text value=\"=\" /><text value=\"&quot;https://mimo.org&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"Learn to Code\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"a\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"1\" /><option startIndex=\"1\" endIndex=\"2\" /><option startIndex=\"3\" endIndex=\"7\" /><option startIndex=\"7\" endIndex=\"8\" /><option startIndex=\"8\" endIndex=\"26\" /><option startIndex=\"26\" endIndex=\"27\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>&lt;</code> seguido de <code>a</code> e depois <code>href</code>, <code>=</code>, <code>\"https://mimo.org\"</code>, <code>&gt;</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
