            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Adicione o atributo e seu valor para que, ao clicar no link, os usuários sejam direcionados para o site do Facebook.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"html\" name=\"index.html\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"&lt;\" /><text value=\"a\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"href\" class=\"attr\" /><text value=\"=\" /><text value=\"&quot;https://facebook.com&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /><text value=\"Like us on Facebook\" /><text value=\"&lt;/\" /><text value=\"a\" class=\"name\" /><text value=\"&gt;\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"3\" endIndex=\"7\" /><option startIndex=\"7\" endIndex=\"8\" /><option startIndex=\"8\" endIndex=\"30\" /></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>href</code> seguido de <code>=</code> e finalmente <code>\"https://facebook.com\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
